  "description": "A setting is the fictional world where a [role-playing game](../index.md) takes place. It encompasses the geography, history, cultures, metaphysics, and tone that define the space in which [characters](./character.md) act. The setting provides the raw material from which the [game master](./game-master.md) constructs situations and the players derive motivation for their characters' choices.",
